4.	Explain how you would make a copy of our production codebase so that you can begin developing a new feature from a project plan and how you would share your work with the world as production software.  Please use exact commands for starting your work, preparing for review, and getting it deployed.

Assuming that we are using github

git clone 'To clone the repository from the server'
Then implement the new requirements performing the a/b Test on the additional code implement by me 
commit my changes and push them to the remote repository.

git add 
git commit -m 'Message to describe the change made'
git push origin

check always if there are any changes in the production branch before commiting 
git fetch origin
git merge origin/master

If everything was approved then  
git pull
